data.description: A MUST SEE. This beautifully updated single-family home is ready to be your home, just look at the pictures!!!. This amazing property features 6 rooms 2 full baths and completely updated open concept layout, It was completely remodeled.  It features an updated roof, boiler, water heater, modern all white kitchen cabinets, stainless still refrigerators and electric stove, first level floors with elegant porcelain tiles. new windows and doors, all new appliances (remaining with the property) & solar panels (which will be transfer to buyer). Great location close to all amenities, new restaurants, highways, hospitals, schools, & MBTA. Offers due 4/15 by 4:00pm
